<D>__{turn around.}
<A>__{marion whirls to show off her dress.}
<C>__{jack}
<D>__{you're all i desire.}
<A>__{he reaches for an envelope on the desk. he gives it to her. marion opens it. there are several fifty pound notes inside.}
<C>__{marion}
<D>__{where did you get it?}
