<C>__{jack}
<D>__{i'm not much of a bet.}
<A>__{he drains his glass.}
<C>__{marion}
<D>__{you are to me.}
<A>__{she takes her scarf, puts it round his neck, pulls him seductively towards the bedroom door.}
